Description: AI Shell - a shell with built-in LLM capabilities
 AI Shell is an interactive shell with built-in LLM capabilities.
 This package installs the application code under /usr/lib/aish,
 and vendors LiteLLM/Langfuse under /usr/lib/aish/vendor.
